com.interpss.simu.multicase.aclf
Interface AclfGridOption

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
AclfGridOptionImpl
public interface AclfGridOption
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Aclf Grid Option'. Class for grid computing options

The following features are supported:

  • Return Case
  • Calculate Violation
  • Bus Voltage Upper Limit PU
  • Bus Voltage Lower Limit PU

See Also:
